function wrap_root (text) {
return [
'<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="a0" align="center" nowrap="nowrap">&nbsp; ' + text + ' &nbsp;</td></tr></table>',
'<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="a1" align="center" nowrap="nowrap">&nbsp; ' + text + ' &nbsp;</td></tr></table>',
'<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="a1" align="center" nowrap="nowrap">&nbsp; ' + text + ' &nbsp;</td></tr></table>'
];
}

return [
'<span><img src="/ecompetition/images/arrow3.gif" height="7" width="4" style="margin-right:5px;" />' + text + ' </span>',
'<span><img src="/ecompetition/images/arrow1.gif" height="7" width="4" style="margin-right:5px;" />' + text + ' </span>',
'<span><img src="/ecompetition/images/arrow1.gif" height="7" width="4" style="margin-right:5px;" />' + text + ' </span>'
];
}
